    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at DXC Technology India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Full Stack Developer to strengthen our Delhi-based team.\n\nAbout DXC Technology India:\nDXC Technology India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with DXC Technology India!",
